1
00:00:13,540 --> 00:00:15,780
♪Trap my frame♪

2
00:00:15,980 --> 00:00:20,060
♪Plagues demand I bow in shame♪

3
00:00:20,780 --> 00:00:22,940
♪Snare my soul♪

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:27,100
♪Rules command I swallow my pride♪

5
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:30,620
♪Mock my way♪

6
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:34,060
♪Chained me where I must stay♪

7
00:00:34,420 --> 00:00:36,780
♪Taught me to kneel, not to speak♪

8
00:00:37,020 --> 00:00:41,220
♪And to let my life pass by in silence♪

9
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,100
♪But I heard the wind♪

10
00:00:44,220 --> 00:00:45,900
♪From the sea and the sky♪

11
00:00:46,180 --> 00:00:47,660
♪It said don't bend♪

12
00:00:47,780 --> 00:00:49,820
♪Bow your head, and your chains begin♪

13
00:00:49,940 --> 00:00:51,380
♪You are the wave♪

14
00:00:51,500 --> 00:00:53,300
♪And the wind that won't behave♪

15
00:00:53,380 --> 00:00:56,340
♪How could you be chained?♪

16
00:00:56,740 --> 00:00:58,740
♪Untamed, uncaged, unclaimed♪

17
00:00:58,780 --> 00:01:00,540
♪You're the blade in my gaze♪

18
00:01:00,620 --> 00:01:02,420
♪This world will leave you no space♪

19
00:01:02,500 --> 00:01:04,220
♪Then pierce it with your blaze♪

20
00:01:04,220 --> 00:01:06,100
♪My silent grind♪

21
00:01:06,100 --> 00:01:08,060
♪My aching pain♪

22
00:01:08,060 --> 00:01:10,300
♪Will one day turn...♪

23
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:14,620
♪I am who I am♪

24
00:01:14,620 --> 00:01:18,140
♪My greatest ambition♪

25
00:01:18,220 --> 00:01:21,300
♪If the world can't contain me♪

26
00:01:21,380 --> 00:01:24,940
♪Then I'll break through it♪

27
00:01:25,420 --> 00:01:26,940
♪Become who I am♪

28
00:01:26,940 --> 00:01:28,260
[Wild Ambition Bloom]

29
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:29,980
[Adapted from Stone and Water's novel,
The Uncaged Flame]

30
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:32,980
[Episode 23]

31
00:01:46,070 --> 00:01:48,660
Have you decided to marry me?

32
00:01:49,510 --> 00:01:50,930
Have you dismissed

33
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:52,380
your wife and concubines?

34
00:01:53,150 --> 00:01:54,850
Forget about this.

35
00:01:55,950 --> 00:01:58,490
You come and drive them away?

36
00:01:58,710 --> 00:01:59,980
There's no such thing.

37
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,380
Since you insist, fine then.

38
00:02:03,710 --> 00:02:05,660
That's right.

39
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:08,660
Since you refuse to dismiss them,

40
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,890
after we get married,

41
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,290
I'll still fool around with Wen Zhiqiu.

42
00:02:13,630 --> 00:02:14,410
If you dare,

43
00:02:15,470 --> 00:02:16,820
I'll kill him.

44
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,450
Go ahead and kill if you want.

45
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,780
After all, even if you kill him,

46
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:24,010
there's still be many other men.

47
00:02:24,030 --> 00:02:25,850
So many men in the world.

48
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,690
Can you kill all of them?

49
00:02:28,960 --> 00:02:31,450
I'll also kill you!

50
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,890
What did you do to me?

51
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:43,610
I was wondering what you were doing.

52
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:45,130
You refused the tea

53
00:02:45,150 --> 00:02:46,290
right in front of you,

54
00:02:46,310 --> 00:02:47,940
but drank mine with poison instead.

55
00:02:48,030 --> 00:02:49,890
What is the poison?

56
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,410
A laxative.

57
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:53,940
The restroom is over there.

58
00:02:54,520 --> 00:02:55,780
You foolish woman!

59
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:57,500
Just wait!

60
00:03:10,150 --> 00:03:10,780
Chase!

61
00:03:18,150 --> 00:03:19,690
Where is he?

62
00:03:20,030 --> 00:03:20,570
This way.

63
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:21,290
Go!

64
00:03:52,870 --> 00:03:53,780
Give me the antidote!

65
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,380
No antidote.

66
00:03:55,710 --> 00:03:56,660
Diarrhea ends once it's over.

67
00:03:57,750 --> 00:03:58,610
I don't believe

68
00:03:58,910 --> 00:03:59,410
you...

69
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:03,100
Look, drawing your handgun again!

70
00:04:03,870 --> 00:04:05,610
Always resorting to violence!

71
00:04:06,310 --> 00:04:07,940
Am I your enemy

72
00:04:07,960 --> 00:04:09,010
or your prisoner?

73
00:04:09,030 --> 00:04:11,410
But you keep drugging me.

74
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,220
You make me!

75
00:04:13,710 --> 00:04:15,290
If you had treated me properly,

76
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:17,050
I wouldn't have done this.

77
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:18,980
I've treated you well.

78
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,810
What more do you want?

79
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,410
Then tell me.

80
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:25,100
Have you ever watched a movie with me?

81
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,170
Invited me for Western cuisine?

82
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,410
Walked with me in the rain?

83
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,050
Danced with me once?

84
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:33,140
What are you talking about?

85
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:35,490
I don't want your money,

86
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:36,610
nor your power.

87
00:04:36,800 --> 00:04:38,610
I don't even expect you to support me!

88
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,140
All I truly desire

89
00:04:40,310 --> 00:04:42,100
is to share a genuine, romantic,

90
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:44,980
head-over-heels kind

91
00:04:45,830 --> 00:04:47,780
of a love story with you.

92
00:04:48,270 --> 00:04:49,290
Random love?

93
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:52,020
Oh! So unpleasant!

94
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,170
It's not random love.

95
00:04:53,430 --> 00:04:54,460
Romantic love.

96
00:04:55,680 --> 00:04:57,900
Just like they show in films.

97
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,810
But none of my past women

98
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:03,900
ever made such demands

99
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,540
on me before.

100
00:05:05,870 --> 00:05:07,220
If I were like them,

101
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:09,460
why would you've come
to me persistently?

102
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:11,930
That's true.

103
00:05:13,140 --> 00:05:15,020
So have you decided?

104
00:05:16,140 --> 00:05:16,930
Alright then!

105
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:21,980
Let's have a passionate random love.

106
00:05:22,020 --> 00:05:23,290
No, romantic love!

107
00:05:23,700 --> 00:05:24,460
That means

108
00:05:24,500 --> 00:05:27,100
you'll dismiss your wife and concubines?

109
00:05:27,740 --> 00:05:28,810
But must I dismiss them

110
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,220
to fall in love with you?

111
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,580
Why can't you understand this?

112
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:37,220
Romantic love happens
between only singles.

113
00:05:37,630 --> 00:05:39,850
But if you marry me as a married man,

114
00:05:40,020 --> 00:05:40,930
it will be an illicit affair.

115
00:05:40,950 --> 00:05:41,780
I can't accept that.

116
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:45,810
Hurry up!

117
00:05:45,830 --> 00:05:47,930
Or it'll end up in your pants!

118
00:05:48,830 --> 00:05:50,780
Oh, I must go now.

119
00:05:55,460 --> 00:05:56,140
How boring!

120
00:06:13,390 --> 00:06:14,580
Have you made up your mind?

121
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,170
Never mind!

122
00:06:18,390 --> 00:06:19,700
What do you mean by that?

123
00:06:19,950 --> 00:06:21,700
You won't bother me again

124
00:06:21,830 --> 00:06:23,020
or will go back

125
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,460
and confront your wife and concubines?

126
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:26,930
As soon as I get back,

127
00:06:27,430 --> 00:06:29,580
I'll send them away.

128
00:06:31,270 --> 00:06:33,170
If you can do that,

129
00:06:33,190 --> 00:06:33,980
I promise to share

130
00:06:34,510 --> 00:06:35,900
an unforgettable love story

131
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,730
with you.

132
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,660
Ms. Chu,

133
00:06:42,870 --> 00:06:45,050
I still need to use the restroom.

134
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:47,610
Go ahead.

135
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:16,610
What are you doing?

136
00:07:17,120 --> 00:07:17,900
Coming home.

137
00:07:19,270 --> 00:07:19,900
Where is he?

138
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:22,290
Gone.

139
00:07:22,630 --> 00:07:23,340
Gone?

140
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,810
What did you do to him?

141
00:07:38,360 --> 00:07:39,250
Nothing at all.

142
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:41,170
He took the wrong medicine.

143
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,980
A strange smell at home.

144
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:52,460
You should take a shower.

145
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,730
It really reeks!

146
00:08:02,280 --> 00:08:05,200
[Wen's Pharmacy]

147
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,490
Wang Guodong's wife

148
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:10,580
with several concubines,

149
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:12,700
visited several newspaper offices,

150
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,140
pleading their grievances loudly.

151
00:08:14,950 --> 00:08:17,120
They claimed to be helpless women

152
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:18,700
[Wife and Concubine
Swear Vengeance on Vixen]

153
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,810
and would be dead if abandoned.

154
00:08:20,830 --> 00:08:24,100
And you are that "vixen"

155
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:27,050
who drove them to this dead end.

156
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,700
Hello, Wen's Pharmacy.

157
00:08:39,480 --> 00:08:40,490
Mr. Wang.

158
00:08:41,270 --> 00:08:42,100
I've seen it.

159
00:08:44,120 --> 00:08:44,890
I'm very pleased.

160
00:08:49,390 --> 00:08:50,770
At 7 PM tonight. Okay.

161
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,580
I'll be there on time.

162
00:09:03,600 --> 00:09:05,480
[Santa Ana Hot Springs]

163
00:09:31,670 --> 00:09:33,610
Welcome, Ms. Chu.

164
00:09:46,270 --> 00:09:48,490
Mr. Wang is waiting for you inside.

165
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,250
Mr. Wang.

166
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,220
How's your stomach feeling?

167
00:10:14,910 --> 00:10:15,530
Very well.

168
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:19,580
I'm getting restless while waiting.

169
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,180
Don't worry.

170
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:24,220
I promise your wait will be worth it.

171
00:10:24,960 --> 00:10:25,820
That's perfect.

172
00:10:26,750 --> 00:10:29,490
Make sure you won't disappoint me.

173
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,850
Take a look.

174
00:10:35,550 --> 00:10:36,460
Come here.

175
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,460
Feel

176
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,460
this atmosphere.

177
00:10:38,480 --> 00:10:39,130
Look.

178
00:10:40,150 --> 00:10:41,370
Romantic enough?

179
00:10:41,750 --> 00:10:42,340
Look.

180
00:10:42,510 --> 00:10:44,650
I spent 50 silver dollars

181
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,220
hiring a foreigner to arrange this.

182
00:10:48,510 --> 00:10:49,770
My apologies.

183
00:10:49,790 --> 00:10:51,100
Have troubled you with expenses.

184
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,980
Never mind.

185
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,220
As long as you're satisfied,

186
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,580
the little sum I spent

187
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,650
means nothing at all.

188
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:08,220
Stand aside!

189
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:10,890
Seems someone is outside.

190
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,060
Don't care about her.

191
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:13,130
Go on.

192
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,420
Move out of the way!

193
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,650
Seems it's your wife.

194
00:11:18,240 --> 00:11:19,650
Those shameless women!

195
00:11:19,670 --> 00:11:21,460
They disgraced themselves
at the newspaper offices,

196
00:11:21,670 --> 00:11:23,490
and now came here to cause a scene.

197
00:11:23,510 --> 00:11:24,220
Step aside!

198
00:11:25,200 --> 00:11:26,850
You vixen! Vixen!

199
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:27,980
Vixen!

200
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,770
Seize her! Don't let her escape!

201
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,340
Vixen! Grab her!

202
00:11:32,030 --> 00:11:33,580
She's running away!

203
00:11:34,270 --> 00:11:35,060
She's escaping!

204
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:36,370
Don't stop us!

205
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:37,220
Darling.

206
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:38,220
Catch her!

207
00:11:39,550 --> 00:11:40,460
Behave yourself.

208
00:11:40,480 --> 00:11:41,730
Don't let her escape!

209
00:11:42,270 --> 00:11:43,730
Drive them out!

210
00:11:44,030 --> 00:11:45,420
Chase them away!

211
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,060
Come out here!

212
00:11:49,550 --> 00:11:50,610
Vixen, don't hide in there!

213
00:11:50,630 --> 00:11:51,340
Come out!

214
00:11:51,630 --> 00:11:52,650
Don't hide inside!

215
00:11:52,670 --> 00:11:53,940
Come out now!

216
00:11:54,240 --> 00:11:55,100
Come out!

217
00:11:55,390 --> 00:11:56,100
Open the door!

218
00:11:56,120 --> 00:11:56,610
Come out!

219
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:58,980
What do you want to do?

220
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,180
How ruthless!

221
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,770
Explain this to me now!

222
00:12:14,910 --> 00:12:17,370
Who on earth is this vixen?

223
00:12:17,390 --> 00:12:18,250
What is she?

224
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:19,300
Hand her over now.

225
00:12:20,150 --> 00:12:21,490
Come out now!

226
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,130
Murder!

227
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,820
That's terrifying!

228
00:12:47,960 --> 00:12:49,060
He is dead!

229
00:12:49,080 --> 00:12:50,250
Nobody moves!

230
00:12:50,480 --> 00:12:51,060
Stay put!

231
00:12:51,480 --> 00:12:52,650
Go back. Don't leave.

232
00:12:52,870 --> 00:12:53,730
All go back.

233
00:12:53,750 --> 00:12:55,420
Move back.

234
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,770
No one leaves.

235
00:12:56,790 --> 00:12:57,980
Head back.

236
00:12:58,000 --> 00:12:59,250
Move back.

237
00:12:59,270 --> 00:12:59,980
Shaohua,

238
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,530
go with me.

239
00:13:00,550 --> 00:13:01,770
No one leaves.

240
00:13:03,000 --> 00:13:03,460
Go back.

241
00:13:04,270 --> 00:13:05,940
Do not move.

242
00:13:06,720 --> 00:13:07,610
Go back.

243
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,060
There is a murder.

244
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,250
Get in the car.

245
00:13:18,640 --> 00:13:19,840
[Rongshun Hotel]

246
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,460
Mr. Xia,

247
00:13:20,480 --> 00:13:22,130
thanks to your resourcefulness,

248
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:24,250
or I wouldn't have escaped.

249
00:13:24,550 --> 00:13:25,300
My deepest gratitude.

250
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:27,980
Ms. Chu, you're too kind.

251
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:31,130
Firstly, as an old friend

252
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:33,650
and Wen's Pharmacy's shareholder,

253
00:13:34,030 --> 00:13:35,220
I wouldn't just sit idly by.

254
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:36,730
Secondly,

255
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,370
given your sharp intellect

256
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:40,610
and connection with Mr. Lu,

257
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:42,100
you'd escape

258
00:13:42,270 --> 00:13:43,460
even without my intervention.

259
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,650
Cheers.

260
00:13:51,000 --> 00:13:51,650
Erniu,

261
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:53,220
thanks go out to you. too.

262
00:13:53,750 --> 00:13:54,890
Without you,

263
00:13:55,670 --> 00:13:57,010
we'd be sunk.

264
00:13:57,630 --> 00:13:59,180
I truly did nothing!

265
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:00,650
Just happened to overhear

266
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:02,530
he would meet you at the hot springs.

267
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:03,580
By chance,

268
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,460
I saw his sixth concubine
at the department store.

269
00:14:05,550 --> 00:14:07,370
Over coffee with her,

270
00:14:07,840 --> 00:14:08,650
your secret slipped out

271
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,180
unintentionally.

272
00:14:10,790 --> 00:14:11,220
By accident,

273
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:13,060
knocked over their jealousy flask.

274
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:13,850
Alright then.

275
00:14:13,870 --> 00:14:16,250
Here is

276
00:14:16,270 --> 00:14:17,530
to these coincidences.

277
00:14:17,550 --> 00:14:18,100
Cheers.

278
00:14:27,350 --> 00:14:28,180
Nearly overlooked you!

279
00:14:28,470 --> 00:14:29,300
Here, Mr. Wen.

280
00:14:29,320 --> 00:14:30,610
Let's skip the small talk.

281
00:14:30,800 --> 00:14:31,610
It's all in the drink now.

282
00:14:32,470 --> 00:14:33,330
Say something,

283
00:14:34,040 --> 00:14:36,180
like "my deepest thanks to Mr. Wen",

284
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:37,260
"exemplifying grace under fire",

285
00:14:37,750 --> 00:14:38,540
"masterful crisis management",

286
00:14:39,280 --> 00:14:40,380
and "turning the tide".

287
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,300
No!

288
00:14:41,710 --> 00:14:43,380
Too cheesy for my taste.

289
00:14:43,510 --> 00:14:44,610
Come on, let's toast!

290
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,570
Mr. Xia, tuck into this feast.

291
00:14:47,960 --> 00:14:48,570
Alright.

292
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,210
Oh, where's Wang?

293
00:14:52,160 --> 00:14:53,900
All sorted. He'll be well taken care of.

