Hurry up!

584
00:27:01,820 --> 00:27:02,580
He has been shadowed

585
00:27:02,580 --> 00:27:04,260
by the manager of Tian's Apothecary.

586
00:27:04,460 --> 00:27:05,660
All his expenses

587
00:27:05,780 --> 00:27:07,220
are fully covered by Tian's Apothecary.

588
00:27:08,100 --> 00:27:09,380
Tian's Apothecary?

589
00:27:09,700 --> 00:27:10,300
Yes.

590
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:12,780
Tian's Apothecary is Mr. Jin's partner.

591
00:27:12,780 --> 00:27:14,420
If we're going to touch anyone of them,

592
00:27:14,580 --> 00:27:15,980
shouldn't we run it by him first?

593
00:27:16,900 --> 00:27:18,180
Have you bought newspapers as I said?

594
00:27:18,180 --> 00:27:18,580
We bought some,

595
00:27:18,580 --> 00:27:19,540
but not all yet.

596
00:27:19,660 --> 00:27:21,060
I told you to buy every last copy?

597
00:27:21,060 --> 00:27:22,260
The press ran an extra print run today,

598
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:23,260
and several other news outlets

599
00:27:23,260 --> 00:27:24,460
have also made reports.

600
00:27:26,660 --> 00:27:27,740
Pushing their luck!

601
00:27:29,820 --> 00:27:30,780
Stand still!

602
00:27:32,420 --> 00:27:33,020
Master!

603
00:27:33,260 --> 00:27:34,740
You're gonna smash
the newspaper offices?

604
00:27:35,940 --> 00:27:37,540
What does it have to do with you?

605
00:27:37,780 --> 00:27:39,340
The reporters are out of line!

606
00:27:40,180 --> 00:27:40,940
Ziru,

607
00:27:41,140 --> 00:27:42,740
pretty women are out there.

608
00:27:43,060 --> 00:27:45,140
Don't make yourself a laughingstock.

609
00:27:45,260 --> 00:27:46,060
Don't go.

610
00:27:55,780 --> 00:27:57,220
Failing to locate Bai Bingxin,

611
00:27:57,220 --> 00:27:58,340
reporters interviewed Wu instead.

612
00:27:58,900 --> 00:28:00,300
He blatantly posted his rates.

613
00:28:00,620 --> 00:28:02,020
Any reporter seeking an interview
with him

614
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,500
had to pay five silver dollars upfront.

615
00:28:03,500 --> 00:28:05,580
He has earned some cash.

616
00:28:08,340 --> 00:28:09,180
He's

617
00:28:09,500 --> 00:28:11,100
got a sharp mind indeed.

618
00:28:12,260 --> 00:28:12,980
Besides,

619
00:28:13,260 --> 00:28:15,340
a reporter from Damai News

620
00:28:15,340 --> 00:28:16,700
even traveled all the way to Peking,

621
00:28:17,620 --> 00:28:19,900
and interviewed Madam Yan
of Linfang Pavilion.

622
00:28:20,440 --> 00:28:22,090
[Popular Prostitute Becomes a Film Star]

623
00:28:22,740 --> 00:28:23,660
Such dedication!

624
00:28:24,660 --> 00:28:26,020
He knows how to work hard.

625
00:28:26,180 --> 00:28:28,380
Madam Yan still remembers Lu Ningxiang,

626
00:28:28,660 --> 00:28:30,740
and said she's become prettier
in Shanghai.

627
00:28:35,220 --> 00:28:36,060
Did this reporter

628
00:28:36,740 --> 00:28:39,740
interview her clients from back then?

629
00:28:40,740 --> 00:28:41,420
Of course,

630
00:28:42,060 --> 00:28:45,020
some even went to gossip magazines

631
00:28:45,100 --> 00:28:47,340
and said they had visited her back then,

632
00:28:48,060 --> 00:28:49,100
revealing a lot

633
00:28:49,100 --> 00:28:50,180
of her sexual affairs.

634
00:28:54,500 --> 00:28:56,060
If Zhou doesn't listen,

635
00:28:56,540 --> 00:28:57,820
push him out.

636
00:28:57,980 --> 00:28:58,580
Got it.

637
00:28:58,580 --> 00:28:59,140
Tongdao.

638
00:29:00,180 --> 00:29:00,820
Tongdao,

639
00:29:01,660 --> 00:29:02,660
have you read the newspaper?

640
00:29:04,220 --> 00:29:04,900
Yes.

641
00:29:05,260 --> 00:29:07,020
The reporters are outrageous!

642
00:29:07,460 --> 00:29:09,140
They're slandering Bingxin
as a prostitute!

643
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:11,020
It's not slander,

644
00:29:11,500 --> 00:29:12,460
but the truth!

645
00:29:14,780 --> 00:29:16,060
Truth?

646
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:18,580
Use your brain for once!

647
00:29:18,940 --> 00:29:19,980
Hand me that plate!

648
00:29:25,620 --> 00:29:27,660
So the person Mr. Zhou mentioned
last time

649
00:29:28,780 --> 00:29:29,780
is Bingxin?

650
00:29:30,740 --> 00:29:31,860
Both you and Zhou

651
00:29:32,380 --> 00:29:34,060
have been played!

652
00:29:38,180 --> 00:29:38,700
But

653
00:29:40,100 --> 00:29:41,820
as they stirred things up,

654
00:29:43,140 --> 00:29:45,140
will Bingxin kill herself?

655
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:47,580
Anyone daring to deceive the Tian family

656
00:29:47,980 --> 00:29:49,100
deserves nothing less than death!

657
00:29:51,540 --> 00:29:52,220
Eat.

658
00:29:56,020 --> 00:29:59,420
[Jujing Apothecary]

659
00:30:02,060 --> 00:30:03,140
As you instructed,

660
00:30:03,500 --> 00:30:04,900
ground two liang
of raw Fuzi into powder.

661
00:30:04,900 --> 00:30:05,660
Here it is.

662
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:07,940
Keep the change.

663
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:10,220
Miss, why are you buying

664
00:30:10,220 --> 00:30:11,100
so much raw Fuzi?

665
00:30:11,260 --> 00:30:12,340
None of your business.

666
00:30:12,500 --> 00:30:13,900
But raw Fuzi is highly toxic!

667
00:30:15,140 --> 00:30:15,820
Thank you.

668
00:30:30,900 --> 00:30:32,260
The clerk didn't recognize her at first.

669
00:30:32,260 --> 00:30:33,740
By when he realized it was Miss Bai,

670
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:34,620
she had already left.

671
00:30:34,900 --> 00:30:35,980
When did this happen?

672
00:30:36,140 --> 00:30:37,260
About two hours ago.

673
00:30:38,140 --> 00:30:39,500
What did she buy?

674
00:30:41,500 --> 00:30:42,580
Only raw Fuzi.

675
00:30:45,140 --> 00:30:46,460
She intends to commit suicide.

676
00:30:47,740 --> 00:30:49,380
Can we drive any faster?

677
00:31:08,560 --> 00:31:13,620
♪Draped in the long night's bitter snow♪

678
00:31:14,300 --> 00:31:21,900
♪Where lies the final destination?
Looking up, is it heaven or the abyss?♪

679
00:31:22,380 --> 00:31:25,780
♪The night watchman
with his lamp is gone♪

680
00:31:26,340 --> 00:31:32,660
♪The light I followed
was but a firefly's deceit♪

681
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:38,860
♪Who judges right from wrong,
and who breaks the judge's gavel?♪

682
00:31:39,260 --> 00:31:46,340
♪If faith collapses,
where do answers lie?♪

683
00:31:47,740 --> 00:31:53,460
♪Black and white entwined,
day and night reversed♪

684
00:31:53,820 --> 00:31:55,540
♪The flame within my heart
can only blaze when fed with tears♪

685
00:31:55,580 --> 00:31:57,860
The clerk said her clothes were neat,

686
00:31:57,860 --> 00:32:00,220
so she hadn't been out on the street.

687
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:05,260
[Jujing Apothecary]
She's probably staying at an inn nearby.

688
00:32:05,260 --> 00:32:06,620
But without much money on her,

689
00:32:06,620 --> 00:32:08,780
she should stay at a cheap one nearby.

690
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:11,060
Split up to search.

691
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:12,300
You take that direction.

692
00:32:12,380 --> 00:32:13,060
I'll go this way.

693
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:13,980
Be careful.

694
00:32:13,980 --> 00:32:14,380
Got it.

695
00:32:20,140 --> 00:32:25,380
[Popular Prostitute Becomes a Film Star]

696
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:27,620
Is there a young lady here
wearing a qipao,

697
00:32:27,620 --> 00:32:29,420
draped in a pink shawl?

698
00:32:29,860 --> 00:32:31,540
About my height.

699
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:33,180
Very young and pretty.

700
00:32:35,620 --> 00:32:36,500
Think carefully.

701
00:32:38,860 --> 00:32:42,020
♪Draining the sun's last glow♪

702
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:48,140
♪On crumbled peaks,
will dawn break anew?♪

703
00:32:49,860 --> 00:32:50,620
Never seen her.

704
00:32:51,660 --> 00:32:53,020
Alright then. Thanks.

705
00:32:55,980 --> 00:32:57,620
Excuse me.

706
00:32:57,620 --> 00:32:59,620
Have you seen a woman
wearing a floral qipao

707
00:32:59,620 --> 00:33:00,900
and draped in a pink shawl?

708
00:33:01,140 --> 00:33:06,670
♪Black and white entwined,
day and night reversed♪

709
00:33:07,140 --> 00:33:12,780
♪The flame within my heart
can only blaze when fed with tears♪

710
00:33:13,220 --> 00:33:18,740
♪Heaven and Earth shatter,
awaiting fire's final breach♪

711
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:24,970
♪Dust of the night
shields the future from decay♪

712
00:33:24,970 --> 00:33:27,540
[Spare Bai Bingxin's Life, by reporter Sun Longyin]

713
00:33:39,180 --> 00:33:41,140
[Emergency Room]

714
00:33:51,020 --> 00:33:51,740
They're saving her.

715
00:33:52,500 --> 00:33:53,340
How's her condition?

716
00:33:54,980 --> 00:33:56,620
More than five qian could be lethal.

717
00:33:57,300 --> 00:33:58,580
She ingested 20 qian.

718
00:34:08,660 --> 00:34:09,500
Mr. Tian,

719
00:34:10,420 --> 00:34:12,060
if anything happens to Bai,

720
00:34:12,060 --> 00:34:13,260
I won't let you off the hook.

721
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:16,980
Mr. Tian?

722
00:34:18,340 --> 00:34:20,220
He brought Wu from Peking

723
00:34:20,220 --> 00:34:21,100
to Shanghai.

724
00:34:21,660 --> 00:34:22,620
At the press conference,

725
00:34:23,380 --> 00:34:24,380
the reporters who attacked Bai

726
00:34:24,380 --> 00:34:25,460
were also planted by him.

727
00:34:26,300 --> 00:34:27,780
Remember the last Claudy case?

728
00:34:27,900 --> 00:34:29,260
He bribed a whole group of reporters.

729
00:34:29,740 --> 00:34:33,020
The same reporters attacked Bai now.

730
00:34:33,180 --> 00:34:34,300
He's behind the scenes.

731
00:34:34,780 --> 00:34:35,820
Family of Bai Bingxin.

732
00:34:35,820 --> 00:34:37,740
I'm her sister.

733
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:39,580
Luckily, she was sent in time.

734
00:34:39,580 --> 00:34:40,900
We managed to save her.

735
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:42,180
Thank you!

736
00:34:57,260 --> 00:34:57,980
Erniu.

737
00:34:58,780 --> 00:34:59,500
Erniu.

738
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:04,340
Am I

739
00:35:06,220 --> 00:35:08,100
still alive

740
00:35:09,180 --> 00:35:11,060
or already dead?

741
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:14,820
You're alive.

742
00:35:15,420 --> 00:35:16,540
Shaohua saved you.

743
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:21,700
Why won't you let me die?

744
00:35:23,380 --> 00:35:24,460
If you were dead,

745
00:35:26,460 --> 00:35:28,420
those who tried to kill you

746
00:35:29,380 --> 00:35:30,620
would have got their way.

747
00:35:30,860 --> 00:35:33,060
So let them get their way.

748
00:35:33,980 --> 00:35:34,740
Why?

749
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:36,820
You've fought so hard

750
00:35:37,860 --> 00:35:39,460
until today.

751
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,340
Why would you give up so easily?

752
00:35:43,380 --> 00:35:44,660
Even if they hate us

753
00:35:45,420 --> 00:35:46,740
and want us dead,

754
00:35:48,220 --> 00:35:49,620
we refuse to die.

755
00:35:51,420 --> 00:35:52,900
Even if it means scraping by,

756
00:35:53,620 --> 00:35:54,980
we come out on top.

757
00:35:55,460 --> 00:35:56,660
But what meaning

758
00:35:58,140 --> 00:36:00,700
does my life hold now?

759
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:04,140
I've lost everything.

760
00:36:10,300 --> 00:36:11,940
Absolutely nothing left.

761
00:36:12,620 --> 00:36:13,780
You still have me.

762
00:36:15,660 --> 00:36:16,420
Erniu,

763
00:36:17,980 --> 00:36:19,580
whatever happens in the future,

764
00:36:19,900 --> 00:36:21,660
you will never lose me.

765
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:23,460
Even if it's for my sake,

766
00:36:24,180 --> 00:36:25,620
you must stay alive.

767
00:36:28,140 --> 00:36:29,820
I have no family left

768
00:36:31,300 --> 00:36:32,340
in this world.

769
00:36:33,180 --> 00:36:34,500
I can't afford to lose you.

770
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:37,460
Shaohua.

771
00:36:37,460 --> 00:36:38,540
It's alright.

772
00:36:39,300 --> 00:36:41,500
We lost everything before.

773
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:42,900
Don't fear.

774
00:36:44,060 --> 00:36:44,820
At worst,

775
00:36:45,700 --> 00:36:46,900
we start over from scratch.

776
00:36:52,380 --> 00:36:53,500
I'm exhausted.

777
00:36:53,980 --> 00:36:55,700
I don't have the strength left.

778
00:36:56,020 --> 00:36:57,580
Then take a rest for a while.

779
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:00,740
You've endured so much hardship.

780
00:37:01,060 --> 00:37:02,220
You've made it through.

781
00:37:03,940 --> 00:37:05,580
You can still manage it.

782
00:37:09,860 --> 00:37:10,900
Can I?

783
00:37:12,660 --> 00:37:13,420
Yes.

784
00:37:14,940 --> 00:37:15,700
Erniu,

785
00:37:18,100 --> 00:37:21,020
you're the prettiest girl
in Qizhou's herb market

786
00:37:21,380 --> 00:37:23,340
and also the strongest one.

787
00:37:40,900 --> 00:37:42,420
I'll start anew.

788
00:37:45,580 --> 00:37:46,580
A fresh beginning.

789
00:37:49,340 --> 00:37:50,140
Bai,

790
00:37:50,580 --> 00:37:52,940
I've rented a cottage for you
in the countryside.

791
00:37:53,380 --> 00:37:54,700
No one there knows you.

792
00:37:54,860 --> 00:37:56,460
When you recover and are discharged,

793
00:37:56,700 --> 00:37:58,500
go there to convalesce.

794
00:37:59,900 --> 00:38:01,860
I'll stay by your side all along.

795
00:38:03,180 --> 00:38:03,940
Thank you.

796
00:38:05,420 --> 00:38:07,140
Once your health improves,

797
00:38:07,860 --> 00:38:10,780
we'll plan our future days together.

798
00:38:11,340 --> 00:38:12,460
Don't be afraid.

799
00:38:13,220 --> 00:38:15,500
Just change your name

800
00:38:15,660 --> 00:38:16,860
and move to another place.

801
00:38:17,340 --> 00:38:18,020
I see.

802
00:38:21,420 --> 00:38:22,220
Wait a minute.

803
00:38:23,180 --> 00:38:25,140
Did she commit a crime today?

804
00:38:25,140 --> 00:38:26,580
Or did she do anything shameful?

805
00:38:26,740 --> 00:38:29,140
Why should she change her name

806
00:38:29,500 --> 00:38:30,380
and move?

807
00:38:30,820 --> 00:38:32,300
Why are those despicable

808
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:33,740
and shameless people

809
00:38:34,420 --> 00:38:35,620
can roam free outside,

810
00:38:36,420 --> 00:38:39,220
while she swallows
her bitterness silently?

811
00:38:40,300 --> 00:38:42,820
I don't want to confront my past.

812
00:38:42,940 --> 00:38:45,060
Your past holds no stains.

813
00:38:45,820 --> 00:38:46,820
I'm defiled.

814
00:38:47,020 --> 00:38:48,460
Those who hurt you are dirty.

815
00:38:48,940 --> 00:38:51,180
They deserve public condemnation

816
00:38:51,660 --> 00:38:52,940
and legal punishment.

817
00:38:53,100 --> 00:38:55,100
You owe no self-blame

818
00:38:55,100 --> 00:38:56,340
or sense of shame.

819
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:59,100
You must not carry this burden.

820
00:38:59,900 --> 00:39:01,620
But others don't see it that way.

821
00:39:01,940 --> 00:39:03,460
You mean those onlookers?

822
00:39:05,700 --> 00:39:07,820
Confused to tell right from wrong.

823
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:09,860
They're nothing but fools!

824
00:39:10,820 --> 00:39:12,100
Why bother caring about their judgment

825
00:39:12,100 --> 00:39:13,260
and vicious talk?

826
00:39:13,420 --> 00:39:14,660
But their vicious talk

827
00:39:14,660 --> 00:39:15,900
will eventually drown Bai.

828
00:39:15,900 --> 00:39:17,580
Then let her stand taller.

829
00:39:17,820 --> 00:39:19,300
You've been writing articles for her

830
00:39:19,300 --> 00:39:20,260
and speaking up for her.

831
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:23,500
If you want to support her,

832
00:39:24,220 --> 00:39:25,460
don't let her hide away.

833
00:39:25,900 --> 00:39:26,700
Stand by her side

834
00:39:27,700 --> 00:39:29,180
and help her face everything.

835
00:39:32,060 --> 00:39:33,460
Face everything?

836
00:39:33,580 --> 00:39:34,180
Right.

837
00:39:35,220 --> 00:39:36,540
Don't need to change your name

838
00:39:38,100 --> 00:39:39,660
or erase your past.

839
00:39:40,380 --> 00:39:43,140
Now more than simply surviving,

840
00:39:44,140 --> 00:39:45,620
you must live even better,

841
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:47,220
more brilliantly

842
00:39:47,860 --> 00:39:49,140
and with greater dignity.

843
00:39:49,900 --> 00:39:50,820
Show them

844
00:39:50,820 --> 00:39:52,060
they can never break you down.

845
00:39:52,900 --> 00:39:54,140
And let them know

846
00:39:55,140 --> 00:39:57,100
you, unbroken despite the wounds,

847
00:39:57,180 --> 00:39:58,780
possess a nobler spirit.

848
00:40:00,380 --> 00:40:01,140
Zhiqiu,

849
00:40:02,460 --> 00:40:03,460
well said.

850
00:40:05,340 --> 00:40:06,020
Bai,

851
00:40:06,580 --> 00:40:08,020
no need to hide away

852
00:40:08,340 --> 00:40:09,460
or live in fear.

853
00:40:09,580 --> 00:40:11,820
Stand up openly and honorably

854
00:40:11,820 --> 00:40:12,900
and expose their crimes

855
00:40:13,420 --> 00:40:16,940
to let them face the just punishment!

856
00:40:31,260 --> 00:40:32,300
[Bai Bingxin Press Conference]
Just received word.

857
00:40:33,100 --> 00:40:35,020
Three more magazine publishers

858
00:40:35,420 --> 00:40:36,580
and two newspapers from other places
will join us.

859
00:40:37,820 --> 00:40:39,700
Then I'll add two rows of benches.

860
00:40:40,140 --> 00:40:41,980
Should we prepare more tea?

861
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:42,740
I'll prepare it.

862
00:40:43,180 --> 00:40:43,900
By the way,

863
00:40:44,180 --> 00:40:46,020
could I get a copy

864
00:40:46,020 --> 00:40:47,100
of each reporter's profile?

865
00:40:47,100 --> 00:40:48,500
Alright, I'll check on it now.

866
00:40:48,500 --> 00:40:49,020
Okay.

